The Best Fresh Tomato Salsa

Ingredients You May Have:
3 cups chopped tomatoes
1/2 cup chopped green bell pepper
4 teaspoons chopped fresh jalapeno pepper (including seeds)
1/2 teaspoon ground black pepper

Ingredients You May Need:
1 cup onion, diced
1/4 cup minced fresh cilantro
2 tablespoons fresh lime juice
1/2 teaspoon ground cumin
1/2 teaspoon kosher salt

Directions:
1. Stir the tomatoes, green bell pepper, onion, cilantro, lime juice, jalapeno pepper, cumin, salt, and pepper in a bowl. Serve.
                            
Nutrition Facts:
Per Serving: 5 calories; 0 g fat; 1.1 g carbohydrates; 0.2 g protein; 0 mg cholesterol; 25 mg sodium.

